Class VolatilCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • fr.inrialpes.exmo.align.service.VolatilCache
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cache
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SQLCache

    public class VolatilCache
extends java.lang.Object
implements Cache
    This class implements the Alignment store of the server in a non persistent way. It can be subclassed by for implementing persistent storage. It indexes all entities in specific tables Allocate them URIs
